@cut_rb
subtitle: +1 resources
on-arrival: resources += 1; rb_strength -= 100; rb_militancy *= 0.93 ; left_strength -= 2; left_dissent -= 2; spd_militancy -= 0.05; workers_kpd += 2; unemployed_kpd += 2; neorevisionist_dissent += 10; neorevisionist_strength -= 5; center_strength += 5; center_dissent -= 5; z_relation += 10; ddp_relation += 8; ddp_dissent -= 1; z_dissent -= 1

Cutting resources to the Reichsbanner causes a drop in the membership, and leads some would-be members to join the Communists instead.


@women_rb
title: Allow women to join the Reichsbanner.
subtitle: -1 resources - This might cause a backlash from existing members.
choose-if: resources > 0
view-if: womens_rights >= 4 and sender_advisor == 1 and iron_front_formed == 1
on-arrival: resources -= 1; rb_militancy *= 0.85; rb_strength += 400; women_in_rb = 1; rb_militancy += 0.05 if repealed_175; rb_militancy += 0.04 if trans_rights; rb_militancy += 0.02 if reformed_183;
max-visits: 1
achievement: women_reichsbanner

The suggestion to allow women into the Reichsbanner is ridiculed by most, except for Toni Sender. But this is an exceptional time, and we need anyone who is willing to join. Thus, we organize specialized units for women, [? if homosexual_rights > 0: and even some covert units for transsexuals and homosexuals ?].

After allowing women to join, the number of comrades who leave is more than balanced out by the number of radicalized women and others who join. However, many of our departed members were veterans, and many of the new members have no experience with military-style training.

@trans_rb
subtitle: -1 resources - This might cause a backlash from existing members.
choose-if: resources > 0
view-if: trans_rights >= 1 or repealed_175 or reformed_183 and iron_front_formed == 1
on-arrival: resources -= 1; rb_militancy *= 0.90; rb_strength += 200; trans_in_rb = 1; rb_militancy += 0.05 if repealed_175; rb_militancy += 0.04 if trans_rights; rb_militancy += 0.02 if reformed_183;
max-visits: 1
achievement: anders_als_die_andern

We have let trans members into our organization.

@same

The Reichsbanner is already serving the purpose it needs to serve. There is no reason to change what already works.

- @return: Continue...
